{"tid":893854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮暫停CNN記者採訪證　CNN：全力支持旗下記者","createTime":"2018-11-08T03:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T04:04:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"90b1c02b5a52b1f3128dd8fc933ff1a08fb69e71","tid":893854,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1427227_1_L_20181108103912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1427227_1_L_20181108103912.jpg&h=3c25447a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮宣布，暫停美國有線新聞網（CNN）記者阿科斯塔的白宮採訪證。<br />\n<br />\n阿科斯塔較早時在白宮記者會向總統特朗普提問，問到有關中美洲非法移民問題，以及會否擔心因為通俄門事件而被起訴，特朗普連環炮轟阿科斯塔，場面火爆，阻止他繼續提問，期間一名白宮女職員試圖取走阿科斯塔的咪高峰，阿科斯塔出手撥開。白宮發言人桑德斯其後發表聲明，指阿科斯塔當時用手觸碰這名工作中的女職員，絕對不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n阿科斯塔在社交網站反駁，批評桑德斯說謊。美國有線新聞網事後發表聲明說，全力支持阿科斯塔，批評桑德斯作出的是欺詐指控，是對民主的威脅。"},{"pid":"0be04efa88f9339b50cd3613a297f66089bbbd8b","tid":893854,"uid":65530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4b344461848a998a19d1e279ccb7d20c2942d3a","tid":893854,"uid":147367,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"派女職員去真係識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fafff83e8a80892766771c1a016b7e6209873a","tid":893854,"uid":59041,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:19:14.000Z","msg":"This is China<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adad7845e09af15701bafc33c0d7a0de73e36e9","tid":893854,"uid":183178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"完全係house of cards劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3920cab63d78cfaa473fda13b0e1a02700808bd6","tid":893854,"uid":217954,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"女權姊妹應該幫邊一